What are characteristics of storage system level virtualization? (Select two.)
A. Storage pools are created from virtual blocks of storage.
B. Virtual disks are created from a storage pool.
C. Virtualization resides in the array controllers.
D. Virtualization resides in the host.
Answer: A,B
